│ parameter. When building the vector of operands, it needs to create         │
│ insertelement instructions, but the insertion point is determined based on  │
│ the fdiv instructions, not their operands.                                  │
│                                                                             │
│ This is a fundamental issue in how the SLP vectorizer handles operand       │
│ vectorization.                                                              │
│                                                                             │
│ Given the complexity, the safest fix is to ensure that when we have         │
│ non-instruction operands, we create the vector building instructions at a   │
│ point that dominates all operands.                                          │
